						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying in front of the Kāḷamma temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Pramōda, Kārttika śu. 1.</hi> However, on the basis of palaeography, it can be assigned to the 17th century A.D.,</p>						

						<p>It registers an agreement of lease of certain lands given to the Reḍḍis and people of Vuluchala by <hi rend="italic">mahānāyaṅkāchārya</hi> Rājavōli Mallinēnigāru.</p>						

						</summary>
